title: First PlayStation 5 Details - Kinda Funny Games Daily 04.16.19
description:
Robinhood is giving listeners a free stock at http://games.robinhood.com

Get 15% off your first purchase at http://thirdlove.com/games

Tim and Greg run through Wired's interview with Mark Cerny and all the PS5 news in it!
